"Note that the schedules table supports the values described in <link linkend="
"\"schedule-values\">Schedule Values</link> above."
msgstr ""
"Merk op dat de tabel met planning de waarde ondersteunt beschreven in <link "
"linkend=\"schedule-values\">Waarden in planning</link> bovenstaand."

